#

Apple Cinnamon Waffles

30 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyEggsGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastBrunchSweetEasy

Description

Fluffy waffles infused with warm cinnamon and sweet apple chunks, perfect for a delightful breakfast.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 ½ cups
  • baking powder: 2 tsp
  • baking soda: ½ tsp
  • salt: ¼ tsp
  • milk: 1 ¼ cups
  • eggs: 2
  • melted butter: ¼ cup
  • apple, peeled and diced: 1 cup
  • cinnamon: 1 tsp
